10 (1) uses or distributes less than ten (10) cubic yards or four
11 thousand (4,000) gallons of organic fertilizer obtained from a
12 confined feeding operation in a calendar year;
13 (2) uses biosolids on land in Indiana that complies with 327
14 IAC 6.1; or
15 (3) distributes inorganic fertilizer to retail facilities.
