21 (3) Indiana NRCS Conservation Practice Standard Code 522:
22 POND SEALING OR LINING – CONCRETE, October 2016.
23 (c) Clay liners must be a minimum of one (1) foot thick and have
24 a maximum specific discharge of one-sixteenth (1/16) in3/in2/day,
25 1.8x10-6cm3/cm2/sec.
