1 following:
2 (A) For processed manure releases or spills to surface
3 water, the nearest affected downstream water user located
4 within ten (10) miles of the spill and in Indiana.
5 (B) For processed manure releases or spills to soil outside
6 the storage structure property boundary, each affected
7 property owner, operator, and occupant.
